{
  "steps": {
    "0": [
      {
        "id": "s0-1",
        "text": "Regions: Kandarin → Kourend → Prifddinas. Kourend is needed for Slayer — have it by tier 6, but it is the weakest of the three for pacts.",
        "type": "info"
      },
      {
        "id": "s0-2",
        "text": "Core problem: Mage accuracy falls flat against some required monsters Solution: Air setup is point efficient; hybrid into melee where magic underperforms (Tekton, Sol, Olm left hand).",
        "type": "info"
      },
      {
        "id": "s0-3",
        "text": "Exception: Olm head still wants ranged — but magic still slightly out dps' vanilla ranged options",
        "type": "info"
      },
      {
        "id": "s0-4",
        "text": "Node strategy: Take all accuracy nodes first, then dip into melee speed attacks as the build matures.",
        "type": "info"
      },
      {
        "id": "s0-5",
        "text": "This guide covers assumed progress only — relic picks are not included.",
        "type": "warning"
      },
      {
        "id": "edit-1776122962122-vgtvq",
        "text": "If taking different regions skip region specific stages!",
        "type": "warning"
      }
    ],
    "1": [
      {
