      {
        "id": "s6-1",
        "text": "Get 95 Slayer for Hydras — this is top priority",
        "type": "warning"
      },
      {
        "id": "edit-1776125739596-lx92r",
        "text": "After getting 95 slayer you can respec into mage with just 19 points! Kill thermy for 20p, take resource and farm the echo weapons!",
        "type": "warning"
      },
      {
        "id": "s6-2",
        "text": "Farm Antler Guard from Slayer tasks — massive offhand upgrade, do not skip mature/elder custodian stalkers until owned",
        "type": "step"
      },
      {
        "id": "s6-p1",
        "text": "Defeat Zalcano",
        "type": "pact",
        "points": 80,
        "region": "Tirannwn"
      },
      {
        "id": "edit-1776125135173-8twr8",
        "text": "70 smithing/mining req",
        "type": "info"
      },
      {
        "id": "s6-p3",
        "text": "1 Skotizo Kill",
        "type": "pact",
        "points": 80,
        "region": "Kourend"
      },
      {
        "id": "edit-1776125076119-q0tmu",
        "text": "Should be easy at this point once you get the totem",
        "type": "info"
      },
      {
        "id": "edit-1776125169864-p9qmm",
        "text": "Decide if you need to respec into 100% ammo throw slayer build",
        "type": "step"
      },
      {
        "id": "edit-1776125244413-c4ceg",
        "text": "Can do with just 16/17 points, will generate chins, depends how fast you are using chins.",
        "type": "info"
      },
      {
        "id": "edit-1776125296032-txt6c",
        "text": "If you do respec, make sure you have atleast 2 reset points and have no more non-chin combat left.",
        "type": "warning"
      },
      {
        "id": "s6-p2",
        "text": "Equip a Dark Bow in Tirannwn",
        "type": "pact",
        "points": 80,
        "region": "Tirannwn"
      },
      {
        "id": "edit-1776124983596-459kz",
        "text": "~1/102 from Dark Beasts",
        "type": "info"
      },
      {
        "id": "edit-1776125412871-nxsca",
        "text": "Awkward without crossbow nodes",
        "type": "info"
      },
      {
        "id": "s6-p7",
        "text": "Equip an Occult Necklace",
        "type": "pact",
        "points": 200,
        "region": "Kandarin"
      },
      {
        "id": "edit-1776125011991-nq178",
        "text": "~1/102 from Smoke Devil",
        "type": "info"
      },
      {
        "id": "edit-1776126376203-jx4le",
        "text": "Kraken tasks might be best left after respec and obtaining echo weps, will become very fast and you can just kill kraken boss for all pacts.",
        "type": "warning"
      },
      {
        "id": "s6-p5",
        "text": "Equip a Trident of the Seas",
        "type": "pact",
        "points": 80,
        "region": "Kandarin"
      },
      {
        "id": "edit-1776124782343-vevvi",
        "text": "Annoying to kill [krakens](https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Kraken#Kraken) trident is ~1/102",
        "type": "info"
      },
      {
        "id": "s6-p6",
        "text": "Equip an Abyssal Tentacle",
        "type": "pact",
        "points": 200,
        "region": "Kandarin"
      },
      {
        "id": "edit-1776124929252-m9kku",
        "text": "1/80 from Kraken boss, much rarer from kraken mobs",
        "type": "info"
      },
      {
        "id": "s6-p4",
        "text": "Defeat the Kraken Boss 50 Times",
        "type": "pact",
        "points": 80,
        "region": "Kandarin"
      },
      {
        "id": "edit-1776124835158-zu0td",
        "text": "Consider leaving this and trident task to last, or after respec.",
        "type": "info"
      },
      {
        "id": "s6-3",
        "text": "If you end up at only 25 pacts, drop echo throw from the build",
        "type": "info"
      }
    ],
    "8": [
      {
        "id": "s7-1",
        "text": "Respec the build for Echo Thermonuclear Smoke Devil",
        "type": "step"
      },
      {
        "id": "s7-2",
        "text": "Kill Echo Thermy on Slayer task — do not forget prayers!",
        "type": "step"
      },
      {
        "id": "edit-1776126761069-cqxet",
        "text": "Wind Wave at 80 magic+ is still respectable here, just remember to turn on all prayers!",
        "type": "warning"
      },
      {
        "id": "s7-p1",
        "text": "Kill 3 unique Echo Bosses",
        "type": "pact",
        "points": 80,
        "isReset": true,
        "region": "Global"
      }
    ]
  },
